column2: "Hey I saw it? Saw what? That rumored black figure!"
"You don't know? There have been reports of several people spotting an all black figure on Naberius."
"I don't know how to describe it, except he really was wearing all black."
"Details? Like I have enough courage to do that! He was creepy enough from a distance!"
"I'm fine with seeing him and coming out alive after that."
